He didn't expect Evil Scholar's Sword
to ruin the steel-made spearhead.

00:18:07.633 --> 00:18:09.341
Before his death,

00:18:09.466 --> 00:18:12.800
he made an invincible spearhead!

00:18:13.050 --> 00:18:15.800
He was worried that the Evil Scholar
would kill the whole family.

00:18:15.883 --> 00:18:17.633
How about the other enemy?

00:18:17.841 --> 00:18:19.133
Who is the next one?

00:18:19.216 --> 00:18:22.091
She was your father's girlfriend.
She fought with me for him.

00:18:22.175 --> 00:18:23.591
But she got married later.

00:18:23.675 --> 00:18:26.133
I don't think you will meet her.

00:18:26.716 --> 00:18:28.675
-Get lost.
-Get lost.

00:18:28.758 --> 00:18:30.216
Don't distract me from gambling.

00:18:30.300 --> 00:18:32.591
Mother, I want to leave home

00:18:32.675 --> 00:18:33.716
for a few days.

00:18:33.883 --> 00:18:36.466
I am afraid the people with King Ning
will come and bother us.

00:18:37.300 --> 00:18:41.050
You should bring along the invincible
spearhead with you, just to be safe.

00:18:41.425 --> 00:18:42.633
Remember.

00:18:43.675 --> 00:18:48.133
-Let's play.
-Come on!

00:18:48.300 --> 00:18:50.216
Since your father lost the duel,

00:18:50.466 --> 00:18:52.341
Evil Scholar's Sword is ranked second

00:18:52.425 --> 00:18:54.633
on the weapon list.

00:18:54.716 --> 00:18:56.758
Our Tong's Spear is ranked third.

00:18:56.883 --> 00:18:59.050
Siu Lee's Dagger is ranked fourth.

00:18:59.216 --> 00:19:00.175
Move!

00:19:01.383 --> 00:19:03.675
Who is the champion?

00:19:04.133 --> 00:19:08.008
The mother of Siu Lee's Dagger,
but she passed away.

00:19:08.550 --> 00:19:11.675
What a pity.

00:19:12.091 --> 00:19:14.508
Cut the crap. Play with me.

00:19:14.591 --> 00:19:16.883
Fortune, bingo. Make it six.

00:19:16.966 --> 00:19:17.883
Drink.

00:19:18.008 --> 00:19:21.091
You are too poor to compete with me.
Get lost, I want to play with Mother.

00:19:22.925 --> 00:19:25.758
-Fortune, make it three. Why not nine?
-Fortune, make it three. Why not nine?

00:19:26.008 --> 00:19:27.466
You lost. Drink.

00:19:27.550 --> 00:19:28.966
I am not scared.

00:19:33.133 --> 00:19:36.966
Come on, bet now.

00:19:42.925 --> 00:19:46.091
Fortune, four and four...

00:19:46.216 --> 00:19:47.633
You lost, drink.

00:19:47.716 --> 00:19:50.883
<i>I am so miserable</i>

00:19:51.175 --> 00:19:54.050
<i>My wives are abnormal housewives</i>

00:19:54.216 --> 00:19:57.258
<i>But others envy me so much</i>

00:19:57.341 --> 00:20:02.550
<i>In fact, I am lonely</i>

00:20:07.675 --> 00:20:10.675
Look, the Four Scholars are over there.

00:20:10.758 --> 00:20:13.258
Go and have a look, hurry.

00:20:49.383 --> 00:20:52.466
You can never escape.

00:20:52.841 --> 00:20:55.008
Pak-fu, it's crowded.

00:20:56.633 --> 00:20:59.591
We came here for a tour.

00:20:59.800 --> 00:21:01.758
That's why the women are that crazy.

00:21:01.841 --> 00:21:02.800
That's why!

00:21:02.883 --> 00:21:06.300
Why don't we have a poetry competition?

00:21:06.383 --> 00:21:07.550
Good idea!

00:21:07.633 --> 00:21:09.175
Why don't you start first, Man-bun?

00:21:09.258 --> 00:21:10.258
I am good in this field.

00:21:11.216 --> 00:21:12.800
There are many geese under the mountain.

00:21:13.300 --> 00:21:15.466
They rushed down to the river.

00:21:15.800 --> 00:21:18.341
Let's roast a goose.

00:21:18.800 --> 00:21:21.175
After eating, go home
and play with your wife.

00:21:21.883 --> 00:21:23.800
Good, very good.

00:21:23.883 --> 00:21:25.008
Very good.

00:21:28.008 --> 00:21:29.925
Is it that funny?

00:21:30.966 --> 00:21:33.966
Why is he always so happy
when he is on a trip?

00:21:34.133 --> 00:21:38.758
I envy him so much.

00:21:39.383 --> 00:21:42.550
He is so good

00:21:42.716 --> 00:21:44.008
at writing poems.

00:21:44.091 --> 00:21:46.508
And he is an excellent artist.

00:21:46.633 --> 00:21:49.050
He is really great!

00:21:49.133 --> 00:21:50.966
And he is good

00:21:51.050 --> 00:21:54.133
at playing music too.

00:21:54.425 --> 00:21:57.216
Right, I know how to play

00:21:57.300 --> 00:21:59.008
all kinds of musical instruments.

00:21:59.133 --> 00:22:00.550
I have studied a new kind of music.

00:22:00.633 --> 00:22:02.841
It's great.

00:22:02.925 --> 00:22:05.425
Let's play it together
if we have a chance.

00:22:05.508 --> 00:22:10.300
-I love it.
-But I envy you because of your wives.

00:22:10.466 --> 00:22:12.175
All your wives are pretty.

00:22:12.258 --> 00:22:15.966
I don't think

00:22:16.216 --> 00:22:20.008
you will have any regrets in your life.

00:22:20.091 --> 00:22:21.966
I envy you so much.

00:22:23.925 --> 00:22:25.133
Bravo.

00:22:28.466 --> 00:22:29.841
There is something attractive.

00:22:31.175 --> 00:22:33.258
Look, there is a beauty.
She seems to be lonely.

00:22:33.341 --> 00:22:36.425
Why not show us

00:22:37.050 --> 00:22:39.508
how to court a girl?

00:22:39.675 --> 00:22:42.508
Let us learn!

00:22:42.758 --> 00:22:43.800
Well...

00:22:44.550 --> 00:22:47.800
It's like a charity for your friends.
Will you do that for us?

00:22:47.883 --> 00:22:49.050
I am glad to demonstrate.

00:22:49.258 --> 00:22:50.258
Go.

00:23:15.050 --> 00:23:16.050
Miss.

00:23:18.800 --> 00:23:20.133
What's the matter?

00:23:22.925 --> 00:23:24.508
-Go.
-Go.

00:23:27.841 --> 00:23:32.841
May I put my head on your shoulder?

00:23:33.091 --> 00:23:35.508
No, I am a girl. A decent girl.

00:23:35.883 --> 00:23:39.466
I know, I want to make
my friends happy, that's all.

00:23:39.591 --> 00:23:41.800
I am Tong Pak-fu.

00:23:41.883 --> 00:23:44.175
So what? I don't know you.

00:23:44.258 --> 00:23:45.966
I'll scream for help
if you don't leave me alone.

00:23:46.050 --> 00:23:48.258
How about I'll pay you one tael?

00:23:48.508 --> 00:23:50.216
Who do you think I am?

00:23:50.300 --> 00:23:51.341
Make it ten.

00:23:51.841 --> 00:23:53.633
That's too expensive.
Why don't you just rob me?

00:23:53.841 --> 00:23:55.216
Right, I am a robber.

00:23:55.341 --> 00:23:56.633
Give me all your money.

00:23:59.633 --> 00:24:00.675
Go to hell.

00:24:00.800 --> 00:24:01.716
Go to hell.

00:24:03.633 --> 00:24:04.800
What's wrong?

00:24:08.925 --> 00:24:11.050
Did you really need to make
a serious punch like this?

00:24:11.133 --> 00:24:12.925
A robber! It's a ladyboy!

00:24:13.633 --> 00:24:14.675
-A ladyboy?
-A ladyboy?

00:24:14.800 --> 00:24:16.175
I love that. Hold this.

00:24:20.300 --> 00:24:22.508
He is faster than me! Damn it.

00:24:45.550 --> 00:24:47.508
Look, so many people!

00:24:47.591 --> 00:24:50.133
Yes, it's crowded.

00:24:50.216 --> 00:24:53.008
Chung-heung, Ha-heung,
shut up and behave yourself.

00:25:02.300 --> 00:25:03.216
What's going on?

00:25:03.300 --> 00:25:04.175
Excuse me.

00:25:04.258 --> 00:25:07.591
Madam Wah and her four pretty maids
have come to pray.

00:25:07.716 --> 00:25:09.800
The maids are all pretty.

00:25:09.883 --> 00:25:11.383
Especially Chou-heung.

00:25:11.550 --> 00:25:13.050
Who is she? Who is Chou-heung?

00:25:13.133 --> 00:25:14.258
Look! That way.

00:25:14.341 --> 00:25:16.216
Chou-heung.

00:25:29.258 --> 00:25:30.675
Damn, she is not pretty at all.

00:25:30.758 --> 00:25:32.133
You know,

00:25:32.300 --> 00:25:34.633
a pretty woman is like a flower.

00:25:34.716 --> 00:25:37.133
You'll be all eyes for her beauty
when some leaves are around.

00:25:37.341 --> 00:25:38.258
Look once more.

00:25:38.883 --> 00:25:40.716
-Pretty woman!
-Pretty woman!

00:25:44.758 --> 00:25:47.050
She is really pretty!

00:25:47.133 --> 00:25:48.258
Let's go to the temple together.

00:25:48.341 --> 00:25:50.050
-To look for fun!
-To look for fun!

00:25:55.341 --> 00:25:56.508
You will be our leader!

00:25:56.591 --> 00:25:57.716
Follow me.

00:25:59.633 --> 00:26:00.841
-Give me.
-Give me.

00:26:00.925 --> 00:26:04.425
Go away, go that way!

00:26:04.841 --> 00:26:07.050
Move aside.

00:26:07.925 --> 00:26:10.716
Let's make use of any chance
to take advantage.

00:26:10.800 --> 00:26:11.883
Sure.

00:26:12.216 --> 00:26:13.508
Give the beggars some bread.

00:26:13.675 --> 00:26:15.133
-Yes, Madam.
-Yes, Madam.

00:26:21.508 --> 00:26:23.008
-Give it to me.
-Give it to me.

00:26:24.966 --> 00:26:25.883
Go.

00:26:25.966 --> 00:26:26.925
Go!

00:26:27.008 --> 00:26:28.341
Be merciful!

00:26:28.466 --> 00:26:31.883
Any kind of bread will do! Come on!

00:26:34.758 --> 00:26:37.716
It's yours, everyone will get his share.

00:26:41.175 --> 00:26:45.091
Don't fight for it. It's yours.

00:26:47.425 --> 00:26:49.008
Madam, this is for you.

00:26:49.258 --> 00:26:53.675
Help! I am damn hungry!

00:26:57.175 --> 00:26:59.008
Are you hungry? Eat this.

00:27:00.466 --> 00:27:02.133
What? Is one not enough?

00:27:04.758 --> 00:27:05.925
One more for you.

00:27:10.383 --> 00:27:12.633
Come over, here's some bread.

00:27:27.800 --> 00:27:31.633
Be good. Come on, eat this.

00:27:59.883 --> 00:28:02.591
<i>I've got it. The prettiest smile</i>

00:28:02.675 --> 00:28:04.300
<i>is a smile with love.</i>

00:28:04.841 --> 00:28:06.466
<i>I have found my dream lover.</i>

00:28:08.508 --> 00:28:09.675
<i>She is Chou-heung.</i>

00:28:42.091 --> 00:28:43.966
Miss, are you here to worship God?

00:28:45.050 --> 00:28:48.591
It's good to worship God.
You will be blessed.

00:28:49.216 --> 00:28:50.466
Let me do it for you.

00:28:57.925 --> 00:28:59.300
To worship God...

00:29:06.675 --> 00:29:08.591
KEEP QUIET

00:29:16.091 --> 00:29:18.716
Hey, chase after the boat of Madam Wah.

00:29:18.800 --> 00:29:19.758
Fine.

00:29:20.633 --> 00:29:22.008
Be careful.

00:29:25.383 --> 00:29:29.800
You are wise to choose my boat.

00:29:30.008 --> 00:29:31.716
My boat is the fastest one.

00:29:31.800 --> 00:29:32.675
Really?

00:29:33.383 --> 00:29:37.425
-Hey, your boat is sinking.
-Right, it's the fastest to sink.

00:29:37.758 --> 00:29:41.550
-What's wrong? I am in a hurry!
-I think you are chasing Chou-heung.

00:29:41.633 --> 00:29:42.591
How did you know that?

00:29:42.675 --> 00:29:44.925
I have seen many of your kind.

00:29:45.008 --> 00:29:48.133
But it's useless to court her
outside Madam Wah's residence.

00:29:48.216 --> 00:29:49.383
What good idea would you suggest?

00:29:49.633 --> 00:29:52.216
You should go to Madam Wah's residence.

00:29:52.300 --> 00:29:55.008
-Suggest me some ideas, please.
-But it depends on your offer.

00:29:55.091 --> 00:29:56.258
All right.

00:29:56.341 --> 00:29:57.591
Listen.

00:30:04.716 --> 00:30:05.550
Hey.

00:30:05.716 --> 00:30:07.925
You can't move. Got it?

00:30:08.050 --> 00:30:10.550
Don't try to trick me. You should pay me!

00:30:10.633 --> 00:30:12.383
How can I trick a wise guy like you?

00:30:12.550 --> 00:30:13.550
That's right.

00:30:15.591 --> 00:30:20.550
Cheap man! A brand new cheap man for sale.

00:30:20.633 --> 00:30:23.050
Come and have a look!

00:30:25.508 --> 00:30:26.675
I'm so poor!

00:30:26.758 --> 00:30:29.175
Hey, young man. Are you selling yourself
to bury your father?

00:30:29.341 --> 00:30:31.341
But it's unlucky to see a dead body
early in the morning.

00:30:31.425 --> 00:30:32.633
I didn't want to do this either.

00:30:32.800 --> 00:30:35.341
You look familiar.
Have I met you somewhere before?

00:30:35.425 --> 00:30:37.675
-Really?
-It doesn't matter, let's be friends.

00:30:37.758 --> 00:30:39.925
Why don't you be merciful? Buy me, please.

00:30:40.008 --> 00:30:41.175
What a pity.

00:30:41.341 --> 00:30:43.883
We need a servant, why not...

00:30:44.300 --> 00:30:46.508
I am poor.

00:30:46.591 --> 00:30:48.966
I am selling myself
to bury my whole family!

00:30:53.550 --> 00:30:54.800
Are you kidding me?

00:30:55.091 --> 00:30:58.466
Be merciful.

00:30:58.758 --> 00:31:01.383
My family died last night.

00:31:01.508 --> 00:31:06.258
I am sick. Why don't you buy me?
I will even make it half price!

00:31:06.883 --> 00:31:08.758
He is poorer.

00:31:08.966 --> 00:31:10.508
Why don't we buy him to be our servant?

00:31:10.716 --> 00:31:12.216
Let's buy him.

00:31:12.883 --> 00:31:14.883
Lady, first come, first served.
I came first.

00:31:15.133 --> 00:31:17.258
-It's not a problem of priority.
-Right.

00:31:17.341 --> 00:31:19.550
He has to bury six people,
but you only have to bury one.

00:31:19.758 --> 00:31:23.050
I want to help you, but it's difficult
for me to buy two people.

00:31:23.133 --> 00:31:24.383
But I am poor too.

00:31:24.466 --> 00:31:26.591
Show me how poor you are.

00:31:26.675 --> 00:31:27.758
Well, I...

00:31:28.758 --> 00:31:31.133
See how dirty my fingernails are?

00:31:31.216 --> 00:31:33.341
I'm very pitiful, right?

00:31:35.716 --> 00:31:37.841
Wong Choi.

00:31:38.008 --> 00:31:40.716
Wong Choi, don't die! Don't die.

00:31:41.091 --> 00:31:45.508
You have followed me for a long time.
You were so good to me.

00:31:45.883 --> 00:31:49.050
But I have never given you
sufficient food.

00:31:49.341 --> 00:31:51.841
I am really sorry.

00:31:55.383 --> 00:31:56.466
Watch out.

00:32:01.716 --> 00:32:04.175
Siu Keung, how are you?

00:32:04.466 --> 00:32:06.175
Don't die, Siu Keung. Don't die.

00:32:06.383 --> 00:32:09.091
We have suffered for such a long time.

00:32:09.383 --> 00:32:12.966
I even treat you like my own relative.

00:32:13.258 --> 00:32:16.508
How can you leave me like this?

00:32:18.216 --> 00:32:20.550
Chou-heung, they are very poor.
What should we do?

00:32:20.883 --> 00:32:22.091
-Let's wait and see.
-All right.

00:32:23.425 --> 00:32:24.425
Damn!

00:32:25.883 --> 00:32:26.883
Hey, wait.

00:32:27.300 --> 00:32:30.133
Look at you. You look rich.
Why don't you go home and put on makeup?

00:32:30.216 --> 00:32:33.841
Look at me. I am thin
and you can see the abscess on my arms!

00:32:33.925 --> 00:32:35.050
I am poorer.

00:32:35.216 --> 00:32:37.341
Buddy, don't challenge me.

00:32:37.425 --> 00:32:38.508
So what?

00:32:38.925 --> 00:32:41.216
-Are you pushing me?
-I am poorer, so what?

00:32:41.716 --> 00:32:42.800
Go to hell!

00:32:43.841 --> 00:32:45.466
Screw it!

00:32:46.966 --> 00:32:50.050
Look, my arm is broken. Who is poorer now?

00:32:50.258 --> 00:32:51.425
Don't go too far!

00:32:51.591 --> 00:32:53.258
It's show-hand, so what?

00:32:54.383 --> 00:32:55.716
I'll play with you.

00:32:56.258 --> 00:32:57.550
Okay, I will show my hands too.

00:33:02.133 --> 00:33:03.300
Are you playing tricks with me?

00:33:03.466 --> 00:33:05.966
I don't want my life either.
Let's see how can you compete with me.

00:33:06.475 --> 00:33:09.350
Who is poorer?

00:33:12.266 --> 00:33:14.641
Bravo! You are really great.

00:33:14.725 --> 00:33:16.975
Hey, he is dead. I can buy you now.

00:33:17.058 --> 00:33:18.225
-Really?
-Right.

00:33:18.308 --> 00:33:20.433
-Another five taels.
-How can you suddenly raise your price?

00:33:20.516 --> 00:33:23.683
I want to bury him too.
You are so kind. Let's buy him.

00:33:24.058 --> 00:33:28.141
Shek-lau, we have to ask
for Madam's permission first.

00:33:28.558 --> 00:33:30.850
-Come again early tomorrow morning.
-I'm going to ask Madam now.

00:33:31.592 --> 00:33:33.800
Thank you, Ms. Chou-heung.

00:33:37.491 --> 00:33:39.450
Such a seducing smile!

00:33:39.575 --> 00:33:41.241
Mother, I did it.

00:33:43.541 --> 00:33:46.625
<i>Since you are so kindhearted,
I'm now buying you to be a servant.</i>

00:33:46.875 --> 00:33:48.250
<i>For six years. Any problem?</i>

00:33:48.333 --> 00:33:49.250
<i>No problem.</i>

00:33:49.333 --> 00:33:51.625
<i>-Sign the contract now.
-I am signing it.</i>

00:34:00.458 --> 00:34:02.333
Mo Chong-yuen has arrived.

00:34:02.983 --> 00:34:04.066
Why don't you squat?

00:34:05.916 --> 00:34:09.000
Kid, from today onwards,
you are a servant here.

00:34:09.500 --> 00:34:12.416
9527 is your number. Start working.

00:34:13.125 --> 00:34:15.750
-Life is difficult.
-Life is difficult.

00:34:15.833 --> 00:34:17.666
But you have to smile
even when you are scolded.

00:34:17.750 --> 00:34:20.208
Life is difficult.

00:34:20.625 --> 00:34:23.250
You have to smile
even when you are scolded.

00:34:23.375 --> 00:34:26.208
-Life is difficult.
-Life is difficult.

00:34:27.291 --> 00:34:31.333
1001, 1002, 1003, 1004...

00:34:31.875 --> 00:34:34.291
How can you do this? Once more.

00:34:34.583 --> 00:34:35.958
One, two...

00:34:40.291 --> 00:34:41.416
Hurry up.

00:34:44.208 --> 00:34:46.833
Roast it carefully.
Reserve the best part for me.

00:34:46.916 --> 00:34:48.208
It's time for dinner!

00:35:15.958 --> 00:35:19.125
SERVANTS AND DOGS ARE NOT ALLOWED TO ENTER

00:35:22.041 --> 00:35:23.958
Higher, fly it higher.

00:35:24.166 --> 00:35:25.458
It's fun.

00:35:25.541 --> 00:35:27.000
Here's a chance.

00:35:33.125 --> 00:35:34.166
It's cut!

00:35:34.250 --> 00:35:36.125
-What should I do?
-What happened, miss?

00:35:36.458 --> 00:35:39.166
9527, get the kite down for us.

00:35:39.375 --> 00:35:41.875
-Right. Hurry up.
-I'm a low-ranking servant.

00:35:41.958 --> 00:35:43.250
I'm not allowed to enter this place.

00:35:43.375 --> 00:35:44.916
We don't treat you
as a low-ranking servant.

00:35:45.000 --> 00:35:46.625
I just treat you like a dog!

00:35:46.916 --> 00:35:49.583
-Go and get it, go!
-Go.

00:35:50.166 --> 00:35:51.583
Up there.

00:35:52.583 --> 00:35:53.958
Ms. Chou-heung, nice to meet you.

00:35:54.500 --> 00:35:56.750
I didn't have a chance to thank you.

00:35:56.833 --> 00:35:58.375
But it's destiny for us to meet again.

00:35:58.458 --> 00:36:00.291
Don't worry about the kite.
I will get it for you.

00:36:00.375 --> 00:36:02.791
-Cut the crap. Go and get it now.
-Okay.

00:36:07.500 --> 00:36:09.625
