00:51:39.191 --> 00:51:40.066
WAH'S RESIDENCE

00:51:40.233 --> 00:51:42.566
I want Chou-heung to get the ink for me.

00:51:42.900 --> 00:51:44.858
Do you want to fight with me
for Chou-heung?

00:51:44.941 --> 00:51:47.316
-I am older than you. She is mine.
-That's nonsense.

00:51:47.483 --> 00:51:49.358
-Do you want to compete with me?
-Go ahead!

00:51:49.941 --> 00:51:50.858
Damn you!

00:51:50.941 --> 00:51:53.066
How dare you! Go to hell.

00:51:54.400 --> 00:51:56.358
How dare you!
I want to teach you a lesson!

00:51:58.191 --> 00:52:00.233
For Chou-heung, I won't give a damn!

00:52:03.150 --> 00:52:05.816
<i>I am finally the servant</i>

00:52:05.900 --> 00:52:08.400
<i>This is within my expectation</i>

00:52:08.566 --> 00:52:11.275
<i>I am closer to Chou-heung now</i>

00:52:11.358 --> 00:52:15.566
<i>I am in a good mood, very good mood</i>

00:52:16.441 --> 00:52:17.775
Where are the young masters?

00:52:22.925 --> 00:52:24.175
-Who are you?
-Who are you?

00:52:24.383 --> 00:52:26.466
I am a servant who will help
with your studies.

00:52:27.133 --> 00:52:29.841
You are the jerk
who disturbed my sleep last night.

00:52:29.925 --> 00:52:33.675
Right. You look great!

00:52:33.883 --> 00:52:35.883
I am pleased to serve you.

00:52:36.425 --> 00:52:37.758
I love this guy.

00:52:37.841 --> 00:52:40.383
-I'll treat you like a human being then.
-Get me tea.

00:52:40.466 --> 00:52:42.466
Sorry, there are three things I don't do.

00:52:42.633 --> 00:52:43.758
What are they?

00:52:43.841 --> 00:52:46.425
I won't serve others tea.
I won't wash clothes or clean the floor.

00:52:46.508 --> 00:52:47.925
I won't make my bed.

00:52:48.133 --> 00:52:49.300
Just like us.

00:52:49.383 --> 00:52:52.091
-What do you know then?
-I know...

00:52:52.758 --> 00:52:55.800
how to play all kinds of music!

00:52:55.883 --> 00:52:57.966
I know fortune-telling.

00:52:58.216 --> 00:53:01.633
I know how to court women too.

00:53:02.008 --> 00:53:04.133
-Really?
-Show us something now.

00:53:04.383 --> 00:53:06.216
I don't think it's fine
to show my skills here.

00:53:06.300 --> 00:53:07.758
I think you are bluffing!

00:53:07.841 --> 00:53:09.383
Read our fortunes then.

00:53:09.466 --> 00:53:11.091
I don't think you're capable.

00:53:11.883 --> 00:53:15.050
If I am not wrong,
then you must be mentally retarded.

00:53:15.800 --> 00:53:18.550
-You are so good!
-I admire you so much!

00:53:18.633 --> 00:53:21.091
-May I call you Brother?
-May I call you Brother?

00:53:21.341 --> 00:53:22.466
I don't mind.

00:53:22.550 --> 00:53:25.508
From now on, bring me tea,
wash my clothes and make my bed.

00:53:28.675 --> 00:53:29.758
Wah Man, Wah Mo.

00:53:29.883 --> 00:53:32.508
Why are you kneeling on the floor?

00:53:32.591 --> 00:53:34.841
-We're calling him our brother.
-We're calling him our brother.

00:53:35.841 --> 00:53:39.300
How can you be their brother?

00:53:39.383 --> 00:53:42.675
It's just a joke, please forgive me.

00:53:42.883 --> 00:53:45.383
-No, Wah On. We will follow you.
-No, Wah On. We will follow you.

00:53:46.091 --> 00:53:47.050
Young man.

00:53:47.133 --> 00:53:49.716
How dare you recruit my students?
Who are you?

00:53:50.008 --> 00:53:51.841
-May I know your name?
-May I know your name first?

00:53:51.925 --> 00:53:52.966
No, may I know your name?

00:53:53.050 --> 00:53:55.341
-No, may I know your name first?
-I have to know your name first.

00:53:55.425 --> 00:53:57.591
-I'll tell you mine later.
-I won't, unless you tell me yours.

00:53:57.675 --> 00:53:58.550
No way.

00:53:58.675 --> 00:54:00.300
I come from Sishui.

00:54:00.425 --> 00:54:03.466
I am the teacher of the Wah family.

00:54:03.550 --> 00:54:04.925
Who are you?

00:54:05.008 --> 00:54:06.133
I come from Suzhou.

00:54:06.300 --> 00:54:08.216
I am a mere servant in the Wah family.

00:54:08.383 --> 00:54:10.466
That's all about me.

00:54:10.550 --> 00:54:12.175
How dare you!

00:54:16.133 --> 00:54:21.591
Do you know how powerful I am?

00:54:21.716 --> 00:54:23.966
I will kill everything that's in my way!

00:54:24.050 --> 00:54:25.091
Wah Man, Wah Mo.

00:54:28.508 --> 00:54:30.091
Sir, what are you doing?

00:54:36.541 --> 00:54:37.875
What's wrong with him?

00:54:38.041 --> 00:54:40.666
Father, you accidentally killed
the teacher.

00:54:40.750 --> 00:54:42.541
Congratulations, you killed him!

00:54:43.333 --> 00:54:44.541
No.

00:54:44.666 --> 00:54:47.000
I saw him performing some sort
of incantation to summon the gods.

00:54:47.083 --> 00:54:48.208
He thought he was invincible.

00:54:48.291 --> 00:54:50.375
But he failed,
so he stabbed himself to death.

00:54:50.708 --> 00:54:52.291
Right?

00:54:52.375 --> 00:54:54.166
Yes, that's right.

00:54:54.250 --> 00:54:55.541
-Right.
-Right. Hey!

00:54:55.625 --> 00:54:57.666
-Take the corpse out.
-Yes.

00:54:57.750 --> 00:54:58.708
Who are you?

00:54:58.791 --> 00:55:01.000
-He's Wah On. He helps us study.
-Yes, Father.

00:55:01.458 --> 00:55:03.833
Wah On, you helped me a lot.

00:55:03.916 --> 00:55:04.791
It's nothing!

00:55:04.875 --> 00:55:07.208
I want to promote you
to Senior Studying Companion.

00:55:07.291 --> 00:55:09.833
You're responsible for educating them,
do you understand?

00:55:09.916 --> 00:55:11.083
Thank you, sir.

00:55:12.000 --> 00:55:14.125
SENIOR STUDENT COMPANION

00:56:13.550 --> 00:56:16.091
Wah On, go ahead.

00:56:16.175 --> 00:56:17.633
Come on!

00:56:17.716 --> 00:56:19.758
Wah On, come on.
Just like what you did that night.

00:56:19.841 --> 00:56:21.508
-Fine, listen to me.
-Fine.

00:56:21.591 --> 00:56:23.716
Wah On has two eyes.

00:56:24.008 --> 00:56:28.008
Three ladies have six breasts.

00:56:31.308 --> 00:56:33.558
-What's wrong?
-Wah On is telling dirty jokes.

00:56:33.641 --> 00:56:34.766
Right.

00:56:35.725 --> 00:56:37.016
-Ms. Chou-heung.
-Wah On.

00:56:37.175 --> 00:56:38.633
Were you joking around with others?

00:56:38.758 --> 00:56:40.550
No, I was reciting a poem.

00:56:40.800 --> 00:56:42.633
-What kind of poem?
-Tong Pak-fu's poem?

00:56:43.216 --> 00:56:44.300
Of course not.

00:56:44.383 --> 00:56:46.841
-Tong Pak-fu is my enemy.
-You can't fool me!

00:56:47.050 --> 00:56:48.758
But you are good

00:56:49.133 --> 00:56:52.300
at making such an interesting story
in a limited time.

00:56:53.508 --> 00:56:56.550
Ms. Chou-heung, you are really wise.

00:56:56.758 --> 00:57:00.841
But why did you impersonate
Tong Pak-fu that night?

00:57:03.008 --> 00:57:04.091
Guess.

00:57:06.175 --> 00:57:09.050
I know, you must know Tong Pak-fu.

00:57:09.133 --> 00:57:10.050
Of course.

00:57:10.258 --> 00:57:11.675
Can you introduce him to me?

00:57:11.800 --> 00:57:12.883
I am Tong Pak-fu.

00:57:13.008 --> 00:57:16.591
Don't joke around. I mean it.

00:57:17.050 --> 00:57:20.633
Everybody knows Tong Pak-fu.
He was born wild.

00:57:20.800 --> 00:57:22.383
But he doesn't know me.

00:57:22.675 --> 00:57:24.216
I think you have misunderstood
Tong Pak-fu.

00:57:24.633 --> 00:57:26.800
Being wild is just on the surface.

00:57:27.133 --> 00:57:29.966
But from his poems,

00:57:30.216 --> 00:57:32.716
I can tell that he is a passionate

00:57:33.008 --> 00:57:34.466
and righteous man.

00:57:37.091 --> 00:57:38.091
Hey.

00:57:38.633 --> 00:57:39.925
What are you doing?

00:57:40.341 --> 00:57:41.883
I feel so touched that I want to cry.

00:57:42.341 --> 00:57:44.758
You are a great observer.

00:57:45.050 --> 00:57:47.300
If Tong Pak-fu had a friend like you,

00:57:47.591 --> 00:57:49.341
he wouldn't have any regrets.

00:57:49.758 --> 00:57:51.008
You are lying.

00:57:52.383 --> 00:57:53.675
Ms. Chou-heung.

00:57:54.425 --> 00:57:56.925
What do you think about me?

00:57:57.591 --> 00:57:58.758
I think

00:57:59.216 --> 00:58:00.633
you are a fool.

00:58:01.716 --> 00:58:03.383
Ms. Chou-heung.

00:58:06.258 --> 00:58:08.258
Are you willing to study poems and songs

00:58:08.758 --> 00:58:11.050
with this fool at midnight

00:58:11.466 --> 00:58:13.925
in front of the willow tree?

00:58:25.550 --> 00:58:26.466
Fine.

00:58:26.550 --> 00:58:27.591
Thank you.

00:58:27.675 --> 00:58:28.800
Don't mention it.

00:58:28.883 --> 00:58:30.758
-Goodness!
-Goodness!

00:58:31.008 --> 00:58:33.883
Chou-heung, Tong Pak-fu is caught
by our security, Mo Chong-yuen.

00:58:36.716 --> 00:58:38.216
Help!

00:58:38.300 --> 00:58:40.091
-Shut up.
-Why?

00:58:40.300 --> 00:58:43.091
I met this guy at the market.
He claimed to be Tong Pak-fu.

00:58:43.258 --> 00:58:45.175
He was selling Tong Pak-fu's paintings.

00:58:45.300 --> 00:58:46.966
So, I brought him here to you, Madam.

00:58:51.175 --> 00:58:52.758
It's the painting of Tong Pak-fu.

00:58:52.925 --> 00:58:54.841
I was framed. I am not Tong Pak-fu.

00:58:54.966 --> 00:58:57.466
If you are not him,
why do you have so many paintings of his?

00:58:58.383 --> 00:59:01.425
I stole them
when Tong Pak-fu wasn't at home.

00:59:01.550 --> 00:59:03.341
You say you are not Tong Pak-fu.

00:59:03.425 --> 00:59:04.425
Who are you then?

00:59:04.508 --> 00:59:07.133
I am Chuck Chi-shan, I swear!

00:59:07.216 --> 00:59:08.300
You still won't admit it?

00:59:08.425 --> 00:59:10.383
Fine, Tung-heung.

00:59:10.716 --> 00:59:12.133
Ask Wah On to come here.

00:59:12.341 --> 00:59:15.633
I want him to identify his enemy,
Tong Pak-fu.

00:59:15.716 --> 00:59:16.758
Yes, Madam.

00:59:16.841 --> 00:59:18.300
Wah On?

00:59:23.466 --> 00:59:24.591
Madam.

00:59:24.716 --> 00:59:25.633
What's the matter?

00:59:25.716 --> 00:59:28.425
I talked too much yesterday
that my muscle hurts.

00:59:28.716 --> 00:59:31.425
Identify this guy.
Tell me if he is Tong Pak-fu.

00:59:31.550 --> 00:59:32.716
All right.

00:59:36.716 --> 00:59:38.341
It's you.

00:59:38.508 --> 00:59:40.216
How can you recognize me?

00:59:40.300 --> 00:59:42.966
-I definitely know you. You are Tong--
-Right.

00:59:43.175 --> 00:59:46.300
I am the one Tong Pak-fu wanted to kill!

00:59:46.508 --> 00:59:48.300
If you don't want to die,
you'd better shut up.

00:59:48.383 --> 00:59:51.758
Madam, Tong Pak-fu is always masked
when he does bad things.

00:59:51.841 --> 00:59:53.841
I am not very sure.

00:59:54.341 --> 00:59:56.341
Well, don't miss out on this chance.

00:59:56.466 --> 00:59:58.050
-Kill him.
-Hold it.

00:59:58.300 --> 01:00:01.925
He must be somebody to Tong Pak-fu.

01:00:02.008 --> 01:00:04.425
So why not let him live?
Maybe we can get Tong Pak-fu by using him.

01:00:04.800 --> 01:00:07.216
Well, I can let him live,
but with severe punishment.

01:00:07.300 --> 01:00:09.883
Shek-lau, lock him up in the storeroom.

01:00:11.175 --> 01:00:12.466
Torture him as you like.

01:00:12.800 --> 01:00:14.925
Thank you, Madam.

01:00:15.008 --> 01:00:17.091
-What do you want?
-Bring him in.

01:00:17.300 --> 01:00:19.175
Don't touch me. I am still a virgin.

01:00:25.008 --> 01:00:25.925
How enjoyable!

01:00:35.716 --> 01:00:37.425
Do you want to kill me
to keep your secret?

01:00:37.508 --> 01:00:39.633
Shut up. You'd better run for your life.

01:00:39.716 --> 01:00:40.925
No, I don't want to leave.

01:00:41.175 --> 01:00:44.175
I have good food here

01:00:44.258 --> 01:00:46.466
and I get to sleep with a wonderful woman.

01:00:46.550 --> 01:00:47.716
Are you kidding?

01:00:47.841 --> 01:00:49.966
I mean it. I owe the loan sharks
too much money.

01:00:50.133 --> 01:00:52.175
-This is the best place for me to hide.
-You...

01:00:52.466 --> 01:00:53.591
Someone is coming.

01:01:02.175 --> 01:01:03.383
Are you all right?

01:01:03.800 --> 01:01:05.966
What's the matter, Ms. Chou-heung?

01:01:06.175 --> 01:01:08.466
Are you Tong Pak-fu?

01:01:09.175 --> 01:01:10.883
Why do you ask me this question?

01:01:11.633 --> 01:01:15.341
Actually, I admire Tong Pak-fu very much.

01:01:15.425 --> 01:01:17.175
I want to meet him.

01:01:17.300 --> 01:01:18.675
Please tell me the truth.

01:01:23.966 --> 01:01:26.341
Right, I am Tong Pak-fu.

01:01:28.175 --> 01:01:29.425
What noise is it?

01:01:29.716 --> 01:01:31.300
It's the noise of some animals.

01:01:32.175 --> 01:01:33.425
Shut up.

01:01:36.050 --> 01:01:37.133
Chou-heung.

01:01:38.091 --> 01:01:40.341
It's fated for us to meet.

01:01:41.133 --> 01:01:43.633
Let's have a long chat.

01:01:46.008 --> 01:01:49.133
May I ask you a question?

01:01:49.966 --> 01:01:51.133
Sure.

01:01:52.216 --> 01:01:54.591
But to show that you are sincere enough,

01:01:55.216 --> 01:01:57.050
you have to answer a question first.

01:01:59.508 --> 01:02:01.925
Close your eyes.

01:02:04.133 --> 01:02:05.841
Relax.

01:02:08.008 --> 01:02:12.258
Put your head on my left shoulder.

01:02:14.425 --> 01:02:17.341
Don't be nervous. Don't you trust me?

01:02:20.175 --> 01:02:22.300
Relax.

01:02:23.216 --> 01:02:26.383
Let your face touch mine slowly.

01:02:27.050 --> 01:02:29.925
Right, good girl.

01:02:30.300 --> 01:02:32.966
-I cannot stand this anymore.
-Hey, I am coming.

01:02:33.050 --> 01:02:34.341
Somebody is coming.

01:02:48.341 --> 01:02:49.258
Miss, who are you?

01:02:49.341 --> 01:02:52.758
Don't you remember me?
You just slept with me!

01:02:53.425 --> 01:02:56.466
I am a civilized man.
What are you talking about?

01:02:57.091 --> 01:02:59.300
You tried very hard just now.

01:02:59.716 --> 01:03:01.425
But there was no one else.

01:03:01.508 --> 01:03:04.591
What? I don't care.
I want to play a game with you now.

01:03:04.841 --> 01:03:06.883
The Beauty and the Beast!

01:03:08.175 --> 01:03:09.966
I know Tong Pak-fu now.

01:03:10.966 --> 01:03:12.675
Wah On is even better than him.

01:03:13.008 --> 01:03:14.591
Thank you, Ms. Chou-heung.

01:03:15.175 --> 01:03:16.591
Why are you here?

01:03:17.258 --> 01:03:19.591
I came to watch something. How about you?

01:03:20.008 --> 01:03:21.133
Me too.

01:03:21.341 --> 01:03:22.716
Let's watch together.

01:03:24.633 --> 01:03:25.925
This is great.

01:03:26.341 --> 01:03:27.300
Really?

01:03:29.966 --> 01:03:33.758
Do you think I am nothing?

01:03:36.633 --> 01:03:39.300
-Once more.
-I'll give you more!

01:03:39.383 --> 01:03:42.716
-Move.
-Move.

01:04:04.175 --> 01:04:06.925
Your Excellency,
King Ning is coming with a troop.

01:04:07.800 --> 01:04:11.675
Dear, His Majesty always goes against you.

01:04:12.300 --> 01:04:14.425
In the government meeting,
you are his political enemy.

01:04:15.050 --> 01:04:18.300
He is bringing his troop here.

01:04:18.425 --> 01:04:19.966
I'm afraid he has some tricks
up his sleeve.

01:04:20.300 --> 01:04:22.091
We should be careful.

01:04:22.175 --> 01:04:23.966
Here comes King Ning.

01:04:30.050 --> 01:04:32.175
How are you?

01:04:33.508 --> 01:04:36.883
Thank you for visiting us.

01:04:37.466 --> 01:04:38.758
I heard

01:04:39.008 --> 01:04:41.633
you love Chinese paintings very much.

01:04:41.758 --> 01:04:46.258
I tried very hard to find
Tong Pak-fu's paintings for you.

01:04:46.341 --> 01:04:47.258
Your Majesty.

01:04:47.341 --> 01:04:50.258
Enough. Bring me the paintings.

01:04:50.341 --> 01:04:51.425
Yes.

01:04:53.133 --> 01:04:55.758
It's really vivid! What a nice painting!

01:04:55.841 --> 01:04:58.758
Right? It's so great!

01:04:59.216 --> 01:05:00.800
I have remounted it.

01:05:01.341 --> 01:05:04.050
Look at the king of the birds.

01:05:04.133 --> 01:05:05.716
It looks as if it is alive.

01:05:06.216 --> 01:05:08.800
It really is the king of the birds.

01:05:10.508 --> 01:05:13.716
How could I accept such a precious gift?

01:05:14.008 --> 01:05:15.675
If you don't, you're not giving me face.

01:05:15.758 --> 01:05:16.841
Do you want me to get mad?

01:05:17.258 --> 01:05:18.508
Don't get mad.

01:05:19.425 --> 01:05:23.300
I want to have a look at the painting too.

01:05:23.466 --> 01:05:26.258
All right. Since you love paintings too,

01:05:26.550 --> 01:05:27.841
have a look.

01:05:33.091 --> 01:05:34.758
Chou-heung, come and have a look.

01:05:34.966 --> 01:05:36.216
Yes, Madam.

01:05:37.466 --> 01:05:41.383
This is <i>Peacock</i> painted by Tong Yan.

01:05:41.508 --> 01:05:43.508
But a peacock
is an ordinary bird after all.

01:05:43.675 --> 01:05:47.341
Even though you have remounted it,
it won't help.

01:05:47.675 --> 01:05:49.133
After all, an ordinary bird

01:05:49.550 --> 01:05:52.300
can't become a phoenix.

01:05:52.466 --> 01:05:55.050
Your Majesty, please forgive her.

01:05:55.258 --> 01:05:57.216
She is still new
in studying about paintings.

01:05:57.341 --> 01:05:58.883
Please forgive her ignorance.

01:05:59.633 --> 01:06:01.800
Your Majesty, since they're experts
in Pak-fu's paintings,

01:06:01.883 --> 01:06:05.675
they must have kept
better paintings of Tong Yan here.

01:06:06.341 --> 01:06:07.633
You are right.

01:06:07.925 --> 01:06:10.466
Madam, why don't you show me
the paintings of Tong Yan?

01:06:10.550 --> 01:06:13.008
Frankly, we don't have
any of Tong Pak-fu's paintings.

01:06:13.716 --> 01:06:16.175
Goodness, you are fooling His Majesty.

01:06:16.300 --> 01:06:17.758
-Your Excellency.
-Your Majesty.

01:06:18.175 --> 01:06:21.841
Tong Pak-fu is now
staying in our guest room.

01:06:22.300 --> 01:06:25.008
Chou-heung, please bring Tong Pak-fu here.

01:06:25.133 --> 01:06:26.216
Yes, Madam.

01:06:32.591 --> 01:06:34.133
Madam, here comes Tong Pak-fu.

01:06:34.425 --> 01:06:35.466
Tong Pak-fu.

01:06:35.550 --> 01:06:38.216
I want you to draw a picture of a phoenix

01:06:38.300 --> 01:06:39.800
for His Majesty.

01:06:40.633 --> 01:06:43.550
All right. I want to know

01:06:43.758 --> 01:06:45.133
how nice your phoenix is!

01:06:45.216 --> 01:06:47.550
If you can't draw a nice phoenix,
you might be killed.

01:06:47.675 --> 01:06:49.591
Tong Pak-fu, draw it now.

01:07:00.008 --> 01:07:01.508
It's done.

01:07:06.341 --> 01:07:08.258
Look, this is <i>Holy Phoenix</i>.

01:07:10.258 --> 01:07:12.633
What? It's only a chick.

01:07:13.966 --> 01:07:15.133
Something is missing.

01:07:15.633 --> 01:07:17.466
A halo, right here.

01:07:20.008 --> 01:07:21.050
Look, isn't it holy now?

01:07:21.133 --> 01:07:23.258
Gosh, how dare you fool me!

01:07:28.716 --> 01:07:31.591
Thank you, Your Majesty.
I've always known he wasn't Tong Pak-fu.

01:07:31.716 --> 01:07:34.675
Now, we've found out the truth
from his painting.

01:07:34.758 --> 01:07:36.341
-Take him out.
-Yes.

01:07:39.758 --> 01:07:41.716
I heard you are great at writing poems.

01:07:41.800 --> 01:07:44.675
My consultant wants to learn
something from you.

01:07:44.966 --> 01:07:47.300
No, the others will tease
Our Excellency of bullying your people.

01:07:47.383 --> 01:07:48.300
Right.

01:07:48.383 --> 01:07:50.383
There's no such thing
as ranking in literature.

01:07:50.466 --> 01:07:52.091
This is just for fun.

01:07:52.466 --> 01:07:55.800
If you don't accept this challenge,
I'll lose my temper.

01:07:56.550 --> 01:07:57.591
Begin!

01:07:57.675 --> 01:08:01.383
A for apple and B for boy.
C for cat and D for dog.

01:08:01.466 --> 01:08:04.466
E for egg and G for girl.

01:08:04.716 --> 01:08:06.716
Come on, continue it.
Are you not giving me face?

01:08:06.800 --> 01:08:08.550
I will lose my temper!
Don't make me angry.

01:08:08.633 --> 01:08:09.966
Please let me try.

01:08:10.758 --> 01:08:14.966
Doe, a deer, a female deer.
Ray, a drop of golden sun.

01:08:15.091 --> 01:08:17.883
Me, a name I call myself.
Far, a long, long way to run.

01:08:19.341 --> 01:08:20.966
Great distich!

01:08:22.008 --> 01:08:25.341
-Wah On, you came in time!
-It's all right. Don't worry.

01:08:27.591 --> 01:08:30.300
I am the consultant of His Majesty,

01:08:30.425 --> 01:08:33.800
The Number One Distich Writer,
Tu Chuen-chang.

01:08:36.175 --> 01:08:37.633
I have studied for two years.

01:08:37.758 --> 01:08:41.258
I am a servant here. Call me Wah On.

01:08:41.383 --> 01:08:44.383
Okay. Let me play with you.

01:09:15.091 --> 01:09:18.300
Sorry, we can't control ourselves.

01:09:21.550 --> 01:09:23.341
Let's start now.

01:09:25.508 --> 01:09:28.133
In pictures,

01:09:28.216 --> 01:09:30.383
the dragons and tigers won't roar.

01:09:30.633 --> 01:09:32.966
In chess,

01:09:33.175 --> 01:09:35.341
the horses and the generals can't fight.

01:09:35.591 --> 01:09:37.716
Bravo.

01:09:38.383 --> 01:09:41.716
An A, a B, a C, and a D.

01:09:43.800 --> 01:09:47.466
An E, an F, a G, and an H.

01:09:48.758 --> 01:09:50.883
Wah On! You are a good distich writer!

01:09:51.008 --> 01:09:52.591
Raise another distich.

01:09:52.883 --> 01:09:55.591
See, a jerk standing over there.

01:09:55.758 --> 01:09:59.633
Here, a bastard is sitting before me.

01:10:03.675 --> 01:10:06.300
I am a hero on the battlefield.

01:10:06.425 --> 01:10:09.341
You are a chicken in bed instead.

01:10:11.300 --> 01:10:13.925
I can't be embarrassed
in front of a small potato!

01:10:14.300 --> 01:10:16.508
Let's plant the trees together.

01:10:16.758 --> 01:10:18.925
For the grave of your father.

01:10:19.050 --> 01:10:20.966
My grandmother has prepared supper.

01:10:21.050 --> 01:10:23.216
My godfather has slept
with your grandmother.

01:10:25.175 --> 01:10:26.425
Bravo!

01:10:28.675 --> 01:10:30.341
Writing distich is for fun only.

01:10:30.425 --> 01:10:33.008
But why are you hurt
while playing this game?

01:10:33.091 --> 01:10:35.675
I wonder how powerful the words are.

01:10:37.383 --> 01:10:39.216
Wah On, it's fine here.

01:10:39.300 --> 01:10:42.008
-Go back and clean the floor.
-Yes, Your Excellency.

01:10:42.133 --> 01:10:46.091
Your Majesty, forgive my little servant.

01:10:46.300 --> 01:10:50.591
He stopped you from losing your temper.

01:10:50.675 --> 01:10:53.216
Fine. Evil Scholar.

01:10:53.300 --> 01:10:56.133
Bring the painting granted by the emperor
to show to Mr. Wah.

01:10:56.216 --> 01:10:58.133
-Yes.
-Let's look at it together.

01:10:58.550 --> 01:11:00.550
Please catch the painting.

01:11:01.133 --> 01:11:02.633
Watch out.

01:11:04.216 --> 01:11:06.800
It's not convenient to look at it here.
Let's go over there.

01:11:26.591 --> 01:11:28.800
It's a precious painting.
You'd better keep it carefully.

01:11:29.675 --> 01:11:32.508
We have plenty of time!

01:11:48.550 --> 01:11:50.008
Is Madam in danger?

01:11:50.091 --> 01:11:51.341
Let's go and take a look.

01:11:51.466 --> 01:11:52.591
All right, let's go.

01:11:53.133 --> 01:11:54.675
Madam, how are you?

01:11:57.508 --> 01:11:58.591
What's the matter?

01:11:58.716 --> 01:11:59.591
I won't tell you.

01:11:59.675 --> 01:12:00.675
Ms. Chou-heung.

01:12:02.841 --> 01:12:05.966
-I was punched three times.
-How ugly!

01:12:06.091 --> 01:12:08.508
I was beaten eight times.

01:12:10.216 --> 01:12:11.966
Someone is uglier than me at last!

01:12:12.050 --> 01:12:13.675
Ms. Chou-heung, what happened?

01:12:15.591 --> 01:12:17.341
I was beaten over 30 times.

01:12:17.633 --> 01:12:19.008
Ghost!

01:12:21.050 --> 01:12:22.216
Ghost!

01:12:26.258 --> 01:12:27.675
She's Chou-heung!

01:12:27.841 --> 01:12:29.591
Yes, she was seriously beaten.

01:12:29.716 --> 01:12:32.758
Did she get hurt by the most horrible...

01:12:32.875 --> 01:12:36.125
Yes, she got hurt from the Faceless Kick.

01:12:36.208 --> 01:12:39.208
Damn! She was kicked by me.
I thought it was a ghost.

01:12:39.750 --> 01:12:40.833
Ms. Chou-heung.

01:12:58.791 --> 01:13:00.458
-What have I done?
-You got hurt

01:13:00.541 --> 01:13:02.625
by the most horrible Faceless Kick
and you were in danger.

01:13:02.708 --> 01:13:06.208
Luckily, I saved you with my Beauty Fist
and returned you to normal.

01:13:06.291 --> 01:13:08.333
You are fine now.

01:13:08.916 --> 01:13:11.291
-Thank you, Wah On.
-Don't mention it.

01:13:11.500 --> 01:13:14.291
-Wah On, is my face okay now?
-Your chin is still a little ugly.

01:13:14.375 --> 01:13:15.583
Use more force.

01:13:22.366 --> 01:13:24.533
Chou-heung, your pretty face is back!

01:13:30.801 --> 01:13:32.183
Madam!

01:14:00.000 --> 01:14:03.166
Mr. Wah, I was so kind
to show you the painting.

01:14:03.250 --> 01:14:05.250
Why did you tear it?

01:14:05.416 --> 01:14:07.916
Please don't be mad. I didn't mean to.

01:14:08.000 --> 01:14:10.083
Cut the crap.
You've ruined the royal treasure.

01:14:10.166 --> 01:14:11.458
I will report to His Majesty.

01:14:11.750 --> 01:14:13.708
He will execute your whole family!

01:14:14.208 --> 01:14:15.416
Wait!

01:14:16.083 --> 01:14:18.250
About the <i>Spring and Autumn</i>
you've just presented,

01:14:18.416 --> 01:14:20.708
I don't think it's the real one.

01:14:20.791 --> 01:14:23.000
How dare you fool me?

01:14:23.125 --> 01:14:25.958
It was given by the emperor.
How can it be fake?

01:14:26.166 --> 01:14:27.625
I am going to lose my temper.

01:14:27.708 --> 01:14:30.708
Hold it. In fact, the real
<i>Spring and Autumn</i> is being kept here.

01:14:30.791 --> 01:14:32.791
It has always been kept in our house.

01:14:33.416 --> 01:14:36.041
If you don't believe me, let me show you.
Chou-heung, follow me.

01:14:38.333 --> 01:14:39.416
Your Majesty.

01:14:39.625 --> 01:14:41.666
Fine, I want to know
what you are going to show me.

01:14:41.791 --> 01:14:44.416
You'll be in deep trouble later.

01:14:46.041 --> 01:14:47.708
Wah On, what are you doing?

01:14:47.791 --> 01:14:50.208
How can we have the <i>Spring and Autumn</i>
drawn by Tong Pak-fu?

01:14:50.291 --> 01:14:51.666
What should we do now?

01:14:51.791 --> 01:14:53.208
Chou-heung, please bring me the ink.

01:14:53.291 --> 01:14:55.833
No, we have no choice. Get me the ink.

01:14:55.916 --> 01:14:58.750
-What?
-Get me some ink.

01:14:59.958 --> 01:15:01.541
I have to draw it by memory.

01:15:02.333 --> 01:15:05.208
But it's hard to imitate
the painting of Tong Pak-fu!

01:15:06.416 --> 01:15:09.083
I hope King Ning will be fooled.

01:15:09.416 --> 01:15:10.666
Impossible!

01:15:11.416 --> 01:15:14.166
How will he get tricked by my painting?

01:15:14.666 --> 01:15:17.291
Wah On, you've messed up!

01:15:17.541 --> 01:15:21.000
You will be killed
and so will the Wah family!

01:15:21.791 --> 01:15:22.916
You'd better leave.

01:15:24.458 --> 01:15:26.458
Nobody is outside, go now.

01:15:36.750 --> 01:15:38.083
-Did you paint it?
-Yes.

01:15:38.166 --> 01:15:40.000
I earned my living
by imitating Tong Yan's paintings.

01:15:40.083 --> 01:15:42.750
I've imitated <i>Spring and Autumn</i>
a hundred times.

01:15:42.833 --> 01:15:44.041
Hopefully, it can save us.

01:15:44.458 --> 01:15:46.458
This is for me to survive,
so I have to carry it.

01:15:46.583 --> 01:15:48.833
-How can you draw so fast?
-I was slow this time.

01:15:54.675 --> 01:15:56.925
This is the painting by Tong Pak-fu.

01:15:57.133 --> 01:16:00.050
How can you claim this is true?
What proof do you have?

01:16:00.358 --> 01:16:03.400
Why don't you ask the expert to check it?

01:16:04.150 --> 01:16:05.358
Tu Chuen-chang.

01:16:08.975 --> 01:16:11.475
Are you still alive? If you are,
come and check out this painting.

01:16:12.975 --> 01:16:15.850
-Is this going to work?
-We'll have to take our chances.

01:16:18.225 --> 01:16:20.683
This is really drawn by Tong Yan.

01:16:22.350 --> 01:16:24.641
Are you kidding me? Impossible.

01:16:24.766 --> 01:16:26.141
Look carefully!

01:16:26.266 --> 01:16:30.016
It's true, but it's rather wet.

01:16:32.908 --> 01:16:34.908
The weather is misty, so it's wet.

01:16:34.991 --> 01:16:36.283
Yes, it's misty.

01:16:36.700 --> 01:16:37.950
You may die now.

01:16:38.033 --> 01:16:39.491
Your Majesty, you are too careless.

01:16:39.658 --> 01:16:41.533
How could your painting get stolen?

01:16:41.658 --> 01:16:43.991
Maybe the emperor will execute you
after he finds out about this.

01:16:44.658 --> 01:16:47.325
But we are friends.

01:16:47.469 --> 01:16:48.916
Take this as my regard.

01:16:49.166 --> 01:16:51.333
Keep it safe!

01:16:51.458 --> 01:16:53.708
Otherwise, it may be stolen again.

01:16:54.441 --> 01:16:57.108
Your Majesty, we should leave.
He is difficult to handle.

01:16:58.608 --> 01:17:00.108
Fine, let's go.

01:17:01.391 --> 01:17:02.808
Hold it.

01:17:02.891 --> 01:17:05.266
You said you wanted to lose your temper.

01:17:05.516 --> 01:17:06.850
Remember?

01:17:07.624 --> 01:17:08.749
Good. I'll show you.

01:17:15.216 --> 01:17:16.508
Are you scared?

01:17:21.591 --> 01:17:23.425
Why didn't you kill them?

01:17:23.583 --> 01:17:25.750
That servant is not that simple.

01:17:25.875 --> 01:17:27.166
I was almost trapped.

01:17:27.250 --> 01:17:28.458
What do you mean?

01:17:28.541 --> 01:17:32.250
Your kung fu is the most powerful
in the world, isn't it?

01:17:32.416 --> 01:17:35.500
Why are you scared of a little servant?

01:17:35.791 --> 01:17:38.291
Your Majesty, my sword is powerful.

01:17:38.375 --> 01:17:40.041
I was afraid it would hurt you.

01:17:40.125 --> 01:17:42.583
You humiliated me.

01:17:42.875 --> 01:17:44.833
Your Majesty, I swear.

01:17:45.083 --> 01:17:46.916
In three days, after I recover,

01:17:47.000 --> 01:17:49.333
I will take revenge for you
and kill Mr. Wah.

01:17:50.250 --> 01:17:52.583
And his wife, Madam Wah.

01:17:52.916 --> 01:17:54.541
And the servant.

01:17:54.708 --> 01:17:56.416
And Chou-heung.

01:17:56.916 --> 01:18:00.000
Anyway, kill them all!

01:18:00.083 --> 01:18:01.250
Yes, sir!

01:18:02.425 --> 01:18:04.300
-Brother, are you comfortable?
-Quite comfortable.

01:18:04.383 --> 01:18:07.800
Brother, you have a move
called Beauty Fist.

01:18:07.883 --> 01:18:11.050
Can you use that move to make us handsome?

01:18:11.133 --> 01:18:12.258
Yes, please beat us.

01:18:12.341 --> 01:18:15.008
But you are too handsome!

01:18:15.383 --> 01:18:17.300
But I don't mind being more handsome.

01:18:17.383 --> 01:18:19.758
-Right. Please give me some tea.
-Brother...

01:18:20.533 --> 01:18:23.533
Really? How can you talk like this?
It's our duty to serve you!

01:18:23.616 --> 01:18:25.116
How can you mention the word "please?"

01:18:25.283 --> 01:18:27.533
Don't you take us as your fellows?

01:18:27.700 --> 01:18:29.116
The word "please" will disappoint us,

01:18:29.200 --> 01:18:31.200
causing hormonal imbalance
and fecal incontinence.

01:18:31.283 --> 01:18:33.825
It will drive us crazy
and I might poop on your body.

01:18:34.133 --> 01:18:37.008
It's only a "please."
Don't you think you're a little dramatic?

01:18:37.238 --> 01:18:39.925
-Stop laughing. I'm serious.
-We're serious.

01:18:40.300 --> 01:18:43.050
Understood. You jerks, bring me some tea.

01:18:43.258 --> 01:18:45.675
-Right.
-Right. I love that, Brother!

01:18:45.758 --> 01:18:47.091
Thank you, Brother.

01:18:50.908 --> 01:18:52.033
-Mother.
-What?

01:18:52.241 --> 01:18:53.200
Where are you going?

01:18:53.283 --> 01:18:54.200
To get some tea.

01:18:54.283 --> 01:18:56.658
Get out. I have something
to say to Wah On.

01:18:57.241 --> 01:18:58.283
Okay.

01:18:58.825 --> 01:19:00.783
-Please be seated.
-After you, Madam.

01:19:01.366 --> 01:19:03.283
Wah On, you've done a lot for us.

01:19:03.366 --> 01:19:05.158
Here is a cup of ginseng tea.

01:19:05.408 --> 01:19:06.908
Drink it. It's nutritious.

01:19:07.158 --> 01:19:09.408
-Wah On.
-Thank you, Ms. Chou-heung.

01:19:09.741 --> 01:19:11.408
You're welcome. Drink it while it's hot.

01:19:13.075 --> 01:19:14.408
You are educated.

01:19:14.533 --> 01:19:16.491
I think you should be recruited
by the government.

01:19:16.616 --> 01:19:19.158
Why are you serving in our residence?

01:19:19.450 --> 01:19:22.950
Madam, I don't care about
serving in the government.

01:19:23.200 --> 01:19:25.741
Moreover, you and Ms. Chou-heung
treat me so nicely

01:19:25.908 --> 01:19:28.908
that I wish I can stay
in the residence forever.

01:19:30.200 --> 01:19:32.158
What a wonderful scholar you are,

01:19:32.366 --> 01:19:34.450
Tong Pak-fu!

01:19:39.750 --> 01:19:41.125
Are you talking to me?

01:19:41.208 --> 01:19:42.291
Stop pretending.

01:19:42.375 --> 01:19:46.083
From your kung fu and poetry,
I have guessed something.

01:19:46.333 --> 01:19:49.375
Although I hate your family very much,
you saved me yesterday.

01:19:49.708 --> 01:19:52.916
I am very reasonable. I won't harm you.

01:19:53.041 --> 01:19:54.250
Just confess!

01:19:54.750 --> 01:19:56.583
I am not, but even if I say yes,

01:19:56.666 --> 01:19:59.583
I won't be able to do anything
if you really want to harm me.

01:19:59.708 --> 01:20:02.083
-Do you understand what I'm talking about?
-Yes, I do,

01:20:02.166 --> 01:20:04.208
but you still have to confess one day.

01:20:04.333 --> 01:20:05.500
Make it tomorrow.

01:20:06.416 --> 01:20:07.333
You are so cocky!

01:20:07.416 --> 01:20:08.416
So what?

01:20:08.750 --> 01:20:09.791
Fine.

01:20:10.125 --> 01:20:12.833
I will marry Chou-heung off to you
if you confess.

01:20:12.916 --> 01:20:14.375
-Madam.
-Really?

01:20:14.666 --> 01:20:16.458
You must keep your promise.

01:20:16.541 --> 01:20:17.375
That's right.

01:20:17.541 --> 01:20:22.041
I am the wise and handsome hero,
Tong Pak-fu.

01:20:28.000 --> 01:20:28.916
Madam.

01:20:29.000 --> 01:20:30.125
You are nosy.

01:20:30.625 --> 01:20:33.458
-Madam, you...
-I didn't keep my promise, so what?

01:20:33.625 --> 01:20:35.625
I want you to die now!

01:20:37.916 --> 01:20:41.041
Hey, please stay calm. No weapons, please.

01:20:41.708 --> 01:20:42.916
Are you begging me?

01:20:44.916 --> 01:20:46.916
Tong Tin-ho, you heartless guy.

01:20:47.041 --> 01:20:48.375
I couldn't kill you,

01:20:48.458 --> 01:20:51.500
but I can kill your son
to avenge my broken heart.

01:20:52.375 --> 01:20:53.708
Don't blame me for being frank.

01:20:53.958 --> 01:20:57.333
How can you kill me with these guys?

01:20:57.583 --> 01:20:59.458
Are you kidding me?

01:21:01.083 --> 01:21:02.125
Let me tell you.

01:21:02.208 --> 01:21:05.583
The ginseng tea you just drank is poisoned

01:21:06.041 --> 01:21:11.041
by something called
the Greatest Drug in the World.

01:21:14.375 --> 01:21:17.500
How can you claim it to be
the greatest drug in the world?

01:21:17.791 --> 01:21:21.125
How about my Tong's Killing Pill?

01:21:22.458 --> 01:21:23.416
Bullshit.

01:21:23.500 --> 01:21:26.416
The Greatest Drug in the World
is made of seven venomous insects

01:21:26.541 --> 01:21:29.416
and arsenic trioxide,
under 49 days processing.

01:21:29.708 --> 01:21:32.750
It's tasteless and colorless.
No one can stay alive after taking it.

01:21:33.000 --> 01:21:35.375
My Tong's Killing Pill is made of honey,

01:21:35.458 --> 01:21:37.166
fritillaria cirrhosa, and balloon flower,

01:21:37.291 --> 01:21:39.208
plus snow lotus from Tin Shan.

01:21:39.833 --> 01:21:42.125
No freezing
or preservative ingredients added.

01:21:42.416 --> 01:21:43.958
It's a powerful poison.

01:21:44.916 --> 01:21:46.416
And it tastes good too.

01:21:47.166 --> 01:21:51.583
You will lose your kung fu
after taking my drugs,

01:21:51.666 --> 01:21:55.833
and your blood will flow
in the opposite direction until death.

01:21:56.083 --> 01:21:59.000
At last, you will explode and die.

01:21:59.291 --> 01:22:02.541
Right, after eating
my Tong's Killing Pill,

01:22:02.833 --> 01:22:06.416
you won't be able to move
even one step or smile.

01:22:06.791 --> 01:22:09.708
Otherwise, your whole body will explode.

01:22:10.250 --> 01:22:12.083
It's so convenient.

01:22:12.208 --> 01:22:13.625
To kill a person.

01:22:14.041 --> 01:22:16.041
-And it's easy to carry too.
-And it's easy to carry too.

01:22:16.250 --> 01:22:18.666
Where is it being sold?

01:22:18.833 --> 01:22:22.416
You are lucky. I have one here.

01:22:24.000 --> 01:22:25.541
I don't think it's powerful.

01:22:25.708 --> 01:22:27.708
No, my pill is the most powerful drug!

01:22:28.125 --> 01:22:30.000
What a joke! You are bluffing!

01:22:30.083 --> 01:22:31.666
You don't believe me?
Do you dare to take one?

01:22:31.750 --> 01:22:34.291
-Do you think I'm afraid?
-I don't think you dare to take it.

01:22:34.416 --> 01:22:35.916
-Okay, I will take it.
-Go ahead.

01:22:36.125 --> 01:22:37.750
-All right.
-Eat this.

01:22:37.833 --> 01:22:39.416
How dare you challenge me?

01:22:39.541 --> 01:22:41.500
-Go ahead if you have guts.
-I have guts, of course.

01:22:41.625 --> 01:22:43.750
Watch me.

01:22:47.375 --> 01:22:49.833
Do you think I am an idiot? Eat this?

01:22:51.125 --> 01:22:52.208
Eat this.

01:22:54.125 --> 01:22:56.333
You are not stupid. You are very stupid.

01:22:56.958 --> 01:23:01.000
Now that we are all poisoned,
why don't we exchange antidotes?

01:23:01.208 --> 01:23:02.958
Damn you, are you threatening me?

01:23:03.208 --> 01:23:05.750
Madam, it's not worth to take the risk.
Your life is precious.

01:23:06.083 --> 01:23:08.458
Hey, lock him up in the storeroom.
Let him die there.

01:23:08.541 --> 01:23:09.583
-Yes.
-Yes.

01:23:12.041 --> 01:23:15.333
-Madam, please be merciful.
-Enough.

01:23:15.541 --> 01:23:19.208
Bullshit. I don't think
his poison can kill me.

01:23:19.416 --> 01:23:21.541
If worse comes to worse,
I won't smile or walk.

01:23:37.000 --> 01:23:37.875
Chou-heung.

01:23:38.000 --> 01:23:39.041
Shut up.

01:23:42.000 --> 01:23:44.583
I have stolen many antidotes
from Madam's exercise room.

01:23:44.916 --> 01:23:47.250
See which one of these can save you.

01:23:47.541 --> 01:23:49.541
I appreciate that
you took the risk to save Wah On.

01:23:50.625 --> 01:23:52.208
Wah On?

01:23:53.000 --> 01:23:55.750
In fact, when you drew that painting,

01:23:56.375 --> 01:23:58.000
I've long known your identity.

01:23:58.500 --> 01:24:02.500
I didn't expect that
you would confess your identity.

01:24:03.166 --> 01:24:06.000
Chou-heung,
I have done all that just for...

01:24:06.208 --> 01:24:09.625
I want to ask you a question.
Please answer me.

01:24:09.708 --> 01:24:10.833
What is it?

01:24:11.250 --> 01:24:13.291
Is Tong Pak-fu your nickname?

01:24:14.708 --> 01:24:16.250
No. Why do you ask?

01:24:18.000 --> 01:24:20.666
Pak-fu, Pak-fool...

01:24:21.333 --> 01:24:23.666
It's really funny!

01:24:28.166 --> 01:24:29.916
If you don't want to answer me,
just forget it.

01:24:30.041 --> 01:24:31.000
Thank you.

01:24:31.125 --> 01:24:32.500
What color do you like?

01:24:33.916 --> 01:24:35.750
Many colors. Let's say, yellow.

01:24:36.125 --> 01:24:38.375
Yellow? This color?

01:24:38.689 --> 01:24:39.625
Yes.

01:24:40.291 --> 01:24:42.375
That's why you always follow me.

01:24:42.958 --> 01:24:46.041
Other than drawing,
what hobbies do you have?

01:24:47.083 --> 01:24:48.041
Nothing special.

01:24:48.125 --> 01:24:51.250
Just listening to music
or playing the flute.

01:24:51.458 --> 01:24:54.958
-You know how to play the flute! Great!
-Yes.

01:24:55.625 --> 01:24:57.416
-Let me teach you sometime.
-Okay.

01:24:57.750 --> 01:25:01.291
You are the leading scholar
of the Four Scholars.

01:25:02.750 --> 01:25:04.416
Have you felt any pressure?

01:25:04.500 --> 01:25:05.708
That's a good question.

01:25:06.208 --> 01:25:09.041
It's a huge pressure.

01:25:09.208 --> 01:25:12.500
So I always have a trip
to reduce my pressure.

01:25:12.583 --> 01:25:13.625
I understand.

01:25:13.958 --> 01:25:16.458
Did you invent the Tong's Killing Pill?

01:25:16.666 --> 01:25:20.291
-Of course not. I fooled Madam Wah.
-You are cunning!

01:25:20.916 --> 01:25:22.708
Do you think she has found the antidote?

01:25:22.875 --> 01:25:24.000
It's not here.

01:25:24.208 --> 01:25:26.041
So unlucky!

01:25:26.166 --> 01:25:28.958
I want to ask you,
are you scared of ghosts?

01:25:30.166 --> 01:25:34.000
Tong Pak-fu is despicable.
He made me jump for a few days.

01:25:34.625 --> 01:25:36.875
Madam, since you're not poisoned,

01:25:37.125 --> 01:25:39.291
why don't you set him free?

01:25:39.416 --> 01:25:42.458
Chou-heung, if you weren't
my favorite maid,

01:25:42.958 --> 01:25:45.500
I would have kicked you out of my home.

01:25:46.083 --> 01:25:47.875
Don't mention Tong Pak-fu again.

01:25:47.958 --> 01:25:49.916
-Madam.
-Get out of here.

01:25:52.000 --> 01:25:54.000
I have served you for years.

01:25:55.125 --> 01:25:56.833
You've treated me nicely.

01:25:56.916 --> 01:25:59.083
I can't repay that with my life.

01:26:00.000 --> 01:26:01.458
Please forgive me

01:26:02.583 --> 01:26:05.333
because I'm going to beg you
to let Tong Pak-fu go.

01:26:06.416 --> 01:26:10.083
I wish to be punished
on behalf of Tong Pak-fu.

01:26:13.500 --> 01:26:16.333
Chou-heung, how dare you!

01:26:16.958 --> 01:26:18.375
-Chou-heung.
-Chou-heung.

01:26:19.333 --> 01:26:21.333
If you don't promise me, I won't get up.

01:26:21.583 --> 01:26:22.666
-Madam!
-Madam!

01:26:22.833 --> 01:26:25.750
I won't change my mind.

01:26:26.291 --> 01:26:27.541
Madam!

01:26:27.625 --> 01:26:29.625
What are you doing?

01:26:29.708 --> 01:26:32.875
We are like sisters.

01:26:33.166 --> 01:26:35.958
Please let Tong Pak-fu go
for the sake of Chou-heung.

01:26:36.041 --> 01:26:37.750
-Tung-heung.
-Please, we beg you.

01:26:37.833 --> 01:26:38.958
What do you mean?

01:26:39.041 --> 01:26:40.166
Drag them out.

01:26:40.250 --> 01:26:41.500
-Madam.
-Madam.

01:26:41.583 --> 01:26:43.416
Mo Chong-yuen, where have you gone?

01:26:58.750 --> 01:27:01.125
How dare you mess things up here!

01:27:01.250 --> 01:27:03.416
Mr. Wah has offended His Majesty.

01:27:03.750 --> 01:27:04.916
You were lucky last time.

01:27:05.208 --> 01:27:07.333
But I won't let you go now.
I want to kill your whole family.

01:27:07.416 --> 01:27:09.083
You are not qualified
to mess things up here.

01:27:21.625 --> 01:27:23.875
-Tung-heung, inform Mr. Wah now.
-Yes.

01:27:27.625 --> 01:27:28.916
Go.

01:27:30.583 --> 01:27:31.583
What's the matter?

01:27:31.875 --> 01:27:33.041
Follow me.

01:27:35.075 --> 01:27:36.325
What happened?

01:27:36.408 --> 01:27:38.783
-The Evil Scholar is here to kill.
-Evil Scholar?

01:27:38.950 --> 01:27:41.325
-You should go, it's dangerous out there.
-What about you?

01:27:41.408 --> 01:27:43.825
-Forget about me, go!
-Hey.

01:27:44.408 --> 01:27:45.783
Chou-heung.

01:27:46.200 --> 01:27:49.616
Madam means the world to me.
I'll stay with her no matter what happens.

01:27:49.700 --> 01:27:50.908
Open the door first.

01:27:50.991 --> 01:27:52.325
-Wah On.
-What?

01:27:52.950 --> 01:27:54.033
I love you.

01:27:54.116 --> 01:27:57.033
What did you say? Chou-heung!

01:27:59.016 --> 01:28:00.725
Go and help!

01:28:02.483 --> 01:28:03.816
Where are you going?

01:28:05.525 --> 01:28:07.441
Chou-heung, ask Wah On to help us.

01:28:07.525 --> 01:28:09.400
Only Wah On can help us.

01:28:09.566 --> 01:28:10.941
Wah On has left.

01:28:11.150 --> 01:28:13.483
He is so disloyal!

01:28:15.358 --> 01:28:17.483
Father, Mother has left.
Let's run for our lives.

01:28:17.566 --> 01:28:18.483
Sure.

01:28:20.358 --> 01:28:21.191
Madam.

01:28:21.275 --> 01:28:22.316
Madam.

01:28:27.650 --> 01:28:28.650
Madam.

01:28:28.858 --> 01:28:31.608
-Madam.
-How are you?

01:28:50.108 --> 01:28:51.233
Madam.

01:29:13.400 --> 01:29:15.691
-Wah On?
-He is Tong Pak-fu.

01:29:15.775 --> 01:29:17.650
Be careful! You're still poisoned.

01:29:17.858 --> 01:29:20.296
Don't worry, I got the antidote
from your exercise room.

01:29:20.566 --> 01:29:23.650
I took some time to take a bath
and get changed.

01:29:24.316 --> 01:29:27.275
Evil Scholar,
you tricked my father in the duel.

01:29:27.775 --> 01:29:29.733
Let's see if you can defeat me too.

01:29:31.441 --> 01:29:33.108
So you are the son of that poor fellow.

01:29:33.483 --> 01:29:35.483
That's why you look familiar!

01:29:35.608 --> 01:29:37.358
I have to avenge my father now.

01:29:37.566 --> 01:29:40.525
Tong's Spear should be number one
on the weapon list.

01:30:52.500 --> 01:30:53.875
Watch me.

01:30:57.583 --> 01:30:59.333
Your father was stupid, and so are you!

01:30:59.541 --> 01:31:01.208
Why did you stab me without its head?

01:31:01.833 --> 01:31:04.458
But it's still powerful!

01:31:09.541 --> 01:31:11.750
I've made it powerful
even though there is no head.

01:31:11.833 --> 01:31:12.916
Now, die.

01:31:17.041 --> 01:31:19.375
From now on, our Tong's Spear

01:31:19.458 --> 01:31:21.166
is the champion on the weapon list.

01:31:21.666 --> 01:31:23.083
Wah On, are you all right?

01:31:23.166 --> 01:31:24.541
I am fine, how about you?

01:31:24.791 --> 01:31:28.500
Great. I am so glad you came in time.

01:31:29.208 --> 01:31:32.458
Tong Pak-fu, I have to thank you
for saving our family.

01:31:32.541 --> 01:31:34.416
How can I reward you?

01:31:34.541 --> 01:31:36.958
You are welcome. I only have one request.

01:31:37.250 --> 01:31:39.958
I know, you love Chou-heung, right?

01:31:40.208 --> 01:31:41.666
I will marry her off to you.

01:31:41.875 --> 01:31:43.125
Bravo!

01:31:44.791 --> 01:31:47.750
DOUBLE HAPPINESS

01:31:51.541 --> 01:31:53.791
Why are there so many brides?

01:31:53.958 --> 01:31:56.833
Tong Pak-fu, although I promised
to marry Chou-heung off to you,

01:31:57.083 --> 01:31:59.500
there is one condition.

01:31:59.833 --> 01:32:03.833
Pick Chou-heung among the brides.

01:32:04.416 --> 01:32:05.500
Wah Man.

01:32:07.041 --> 01:32:10.625
"You should find her
before the incense burns out.

01:32:11.708 --> 01:32:13.166
There are several rules.

01:32:13.250 --> 01:32:16.916
First, stand behind the yellow line.

01:32:17.708 --> 01:32:21.250
Second, the brides

01:32:21.500 --> 01:32:23.166
can't make any noise.

01:32:23.541 --> 01:32:28.125
Third, don't use anything
to touch the brides."

01:32:28.375 --> 01:32:29.541
That's all.

01:32:30.000 --> 01:32:32.500
If you can't find Chou-heung
within the limited time,

01:32:32.583 --> 01:32:33.500
you'll lose.

01:32:33.875 --> 01:32:36.625
Then, Chou-heung will marry my sons.

01:32:36.791 --> 01:32:38.708
Brother, we are on the waiting list.

01:32:38.833 --> 01:32:40.125
Don't blame us.

01:32:42.375 --> 01:32:44.750
Madam, please don't fool me.

01:32:45.666 --> 01:32:48.041
Mr. Tong, what do you mean?

01:32:48.791 --> 01:32:50.208
In such conditions,

01:32:50.416 --> 01:32:52.458
how will I be able to find Chou-heung?

01:32:52.916 --> 01:32:54.458
I can speak from my heart

01:32:54.666 --> 01:32:56.916
that I love Chou-heung wholeheartedly.

01:32:57.208 --> 01:32:59.416
Why do you have to trick me?

01:32:59.791 --> 01:33:03.500
Tong Pak-fu, you said you were poor.

01:33:04.041 --> 01:33:06.166
You were willing to sell yourself
to be our servant.

01:33:07.500 --> 01:33:09.291
There was a contract too.

01:33:09.416 --> 01:33:11.750
But in fact, you came here
to court Chou-heung.

01:33:13.250 --> 01:33:15.875
It's you who fooled us first.

01:33:16.041 --> 01:33:19.791
No! Read the first line of the contract
horizontally, please.

01:33:22.083 --> 01:33:23.416
"I came for Chou-heung."

01:33:23.500 --> 01:33:25.291
Yes, I came for Chou-heung.

01:33:25.458 --> 01:33:26.750
I've told you why I was here.

01:33:26.833 --> 01:33:28.458
But you were not wise enough to read it.

01:33:28.875 --> 01:33:31.875
Don't be that cocky.
I want to fool you, so what?

01:33:32.000 --> 01:33:34.000
Fool me? Why don't you go
and study for two more years?

01:33:34.125 --> 01:33:36.458
I'll take her away. What can you do?
No one can stop me.

01:33:36.541 --> 01:33:38.750
Go ahead and try.
This is the Wah's residence!

01:33:38.833 --> 01:33:40.875
I'll ask His Excellency
to sue you in front of the emperor.

01:33:40.958 --> 01:33:42.458
You will be sentenced to death!

01:33:42.541 --> 01:33:44.375
Damn you, how dare you!
You are so shameless!

01:33:44.458 --> 01:33:45.583
How dare you scold me?

01:33:45.833 --> 01:33:46.916
Go to hell!

01:33:47.916 --> 01:33:49.250
Take it back.

01:33:49.875 --> 01:33:51.208
I won't forgive you.

01:33:52.333 --> 01:33:53.500
Come on.

01:33:53.583 --> 01:33:54.750
You bitch! Don't pull me.

01:33:54.916 --> 01:33:55.875
Mother.

01:33:56.500 --> 01:33:59.125
Stop or I will kick you to death.

01:33:59.250 --> 01:34:00.750
Stop!

01:34:01.916 --> 01:34:05.291
Tong Pak-fu, Chou-heung is our maid.

01:34:05.625 --> 01:34:07.125
If you want to marry her,

01:34:07.375 --> 01:34:09.791
you should follow our rules.

01:34:09.958 --> 01:34:11.833
The incense is going to be burnt out.

01:34:12.291 --> 01:34:14.500
Think of something.

01:34:15.541 --> 01:34:18.375
Fine, I will try my best.

01:34:18.541 --> 01:34:20.375
I will find Chou-heung.

01:34:22.541 --> 01:34:24.208
Wonder World.

01:34:44.541 --> 01:34:45.791
Great Waves.

01:34:59.458 --> 01:35:02.833
First stance! Wonder Palm.

01:35:09.375 --> 01:35:10.458
Not this one.

01:35:10.791 --> 01:35:11.958
Once again!

01:35:12.916 --> 01:35:14.416
Substitution.

01:35:24.666 --> 01:35:25.875
In double!

01:35:29.333 --> 01:35:30.208
Damn!

01:35:37.541 --> 01:35:39.208
Tong Pak-fu, are you dying?

01:35:39.375 --> 01:35:40.666
Wonder Palm?

01:35:40.958 --> 01:35:42.416
Not exactly.

01:35:47.958 --> 01:35:50.041
It's you who is making me
use my last stance!

01:36:00.625 --> 01:36:04.166
Turtle Ball...

01:36:04.500 --> 01:36:05.875
It's strong.

01:36:06.041 --> 01:36:07.125
Air...

01:36:07.208 --> 01:36:09.416
He is so powerful!

01:36:09.625 --> 01:36:11.458
Is he Superman?

01:36:11.750 --> 01:36:12.875
Stance!

01:36:28.208 --> 01:36:29.208
What the heck?

01:36:31.541 --> 01:36:32.916
Look, Tong Pak-fu.

01:36:33.125 --> 01:36:36.583
I have something
to fight against your stance!

01:36:36.791 --> 01:36:38.416
Damn you, how dare you trick me?

01:36:38.625 --> 01:36:40.916
I love it, so what?

01:36:42.541 --> 01:36:43.833
Damn you, go to hell!

01:36:43.958 --> 01:36:45.750
No.

01:36:45.833 --> 01:36:47.208
The incense is going to be burnt out.

01:36:47.291 --> 01:36:48.958
Chou-heung will marry my sons.

01:36:53.000 --> 01:36:55.125
Am I destined to be alone?

01:36:55.958 --> 01:37:00.500
My goodness.

01:37:02.500 --> 01:37:04.875
"The people thought I was insane.

01:37:06.208 --> 01:37:08.375
But they don't really understand me.

01:37:08.916 --> 01:37:11.041
Can't you see the graves of the heroes?

01:37:11.916 --> 01:37:14.833
No flowers, no wine, but who cares?"

01:37:19.750 --> 01:37:21.000
I know!

01:37:35.375 --> 01:37:36.541
Time's up.

01:37:36.625 --> 01:37:37.791
Right on time.

01:37:38.875 --> 01:37:40.125
Chou-heung.

01:37:50.916 --> 01:37:54.416
My goodness, why did you tremble
when I recited my poem?

01:37:54.833 --> 01:37:58.250
I didn't! I just wanted to go
and take a leak.

01:38:00.750 --> 01:38:01.916
Do you have a knife?

01:38:02.291 --> 01:38:03.125
What for?

01:38:03.291 --> 01:38:04.333
I want to commit suicide.

01:38:04.458 --> 01:38:07.916
No, you have to marry me first.

01:38:11.041 --> 01:38:14.458
I prefer dying.

01:38:17.416 --> 01:38:21.083
Buddy, how dare you court my girl?

01:38:21.416 --> 01:38:22.833
Your girl is over there!

01:38:32.208 --> 01:38:33.333
Chou-heung.

01:38:33.583 --> 01:38:35.583
Hurry and have the wedding now.

01:38:44.041 --> 01:38:47.625
Tidy up first. That's better.

01:38:47.708 --> 01:38:49.208
Kneel.

01:38:49.333 --> 01:38:51.583
The wedding starts now.

01:38:53.875 --> 01:38:57.625
Chou-heung, after so many tests,

01:38:57.916 --> 01:38:59.875
I believe that
he loves you wholeheartedly.

01:39:00.166 --> 01:39:02.208
Now, I will let him marry you.

01:39:02.708 --> 01:39:03.916
Thank you, Madam.

01:39:05.666 --> 01:39:07.666
Tong Pak-fu, are you satisfied?

01:39:07.916 --> 01:39:09.708
What else do you want to say?

01:39:10.416 --> 01:39:13.875
What an interesting life!

01:39:14.166 --> 01:39:15.500
I want to go and take a leak.

01:39:15.625 --> 01:39:18.916
You're looking forward to
the first night with her, right?

01:39:20.791 --> 01:39:23.708
Tong Pak-fu, don't let us down.

01:39:24.041 --> 01:39:26.291
Treat Chou-heung well.

01:39:26.666 --> 01:39:28.791
Madam, I am sorry.
I have misunderstood you.

01:39:29.375 --> 01:39:31.166
You will always be our brother.

01:39:31.250 --> 01:39:32.875
We wish you a long, happy life.

01:39:32.958 --> 01:39:34.750
Just like today!

01:39:35.791 --> 01:39:36.875
Thank you.

01:39:49.833 --> 01:39:54.958
Chou-heung, after so many difficulties...

01:39:56.250 --> 01:39:58.583
We are married at last.

01:40:01.541 --> 01:40:04.333
Congratulations. You're really great!

01:40:04.500 --> 01:40:06.333
Your wife is so pretty.

01:40:06.416 --> 01:40:09.166
Why don't you kiss your bride now?

01:40:09.666 --> 01:40:11.333
Come on.

01:40:11.708 --> 01:40:12.583
Hold it!

01:40:12.875 --> 01:40:14.250
Play a guessing game with me.

01:40:14.791 --> 01:40:16.000
You don't know how to play?

01:40:16.083 --> 01:40:18.333
How about mahjong,
Heaven and Nine, or Blackjack?

01:40:18.416 --> 01:40:20.000
You should know at least
one of these, right?

01:40:22.375 --> 01:40:26.208
THE END
